<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="NTM13.2">
<l>pālā lilaiyiṟ ṟuyilkoṇṭa paramaṉ valaippaṭ ṭiruntēṉai</l>
<l>vēlāṟ ṟuṉṉam peytāṟpōl vēṇṭiṟ ṟellām pēcātē</l>
<l>kōlāl niraimēyt tāyaṉāyk kuṭantaik kiṭanta kuṭamāṭi</l>
<l>nīlār taṇṇan tuḻāykoṇṭeṉ ṉeṟimēṉ kuḻalmel cūṭṭīrē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Do not speak at will—like one would poke with a spear—about me</l>
<l>who am caught in the nets of the Supreme Being who reclines on the sappy banyan leaf!</l>
<l>[Instead,] do adorn my bristling, soft locks with the pretty, dark, cool tulsi</l>
<l>Of the pot-dancer who lay in Kuṭantai, having become a cowherd who grazed herds of cows</l>
<l rend="indent">with a stick [in hand].</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
